rg.name: Honey Lynn Lynn
rg.affiliation: Kyushu University | Kyudai, Kyushu University, Department of Agricultural  Resource Economics
rg.bio: Honey Lynn Lynn is doing her Ph.D. research at the Department of Agricultural and Resource Economics, Kyushu University. Her current research interests are regarding agri-food value chains, agricultural development, contract farming cases in developing and developed countries, the analysis of optimum profit and utility functions of the players in the contractual games.
